@startuml
title Statechart diagram of the class "Plane"

[*] --> Order
state Arrival
state Preparation
state Operations
state Maintenance
state OutOfService <<final>>
state RemovedFromOperations <<final>>

Order --> Arrival : «M» Plane Acquired/
Arrival --> Preparation : «M» Plane Arrived/
Preparation --> Operations : «M» Condition and Schedule/
Preparation --> Maintenance : «M» No more flights or maintenance required/
Operations --> OutOfService : «M» Permanently withdrawn from service/
Maintenance --> Preparation : «M» Plane Ready for operations/
Maintenance --> OutOfService : «M» Plane Unavailable for use/
RemovedFromOperations --> [*] : «M» Plane No longer in operations/
OutOfService --> [*] : «M» Plane Out of service/
@enduml
